nctional","section":"FPS Payment Flow","title":"Settlement Result Notification to Payer Bank (Step 5a)","description":"The payer bank receives the settlement result from HKICL (transmission format: FIToFIPmtStsRpt (pacs.002)) and notifies the payer of the transfer result.","business_rules":["Transmission format must be pacs.002 (FIToFIPmtStsRpt)"],"acceptance_criteria":["Payer bank receives pacs.002 message from HKICL as settlement result","Payer bank notifies the payer of the transfer result"],"dependencies":["Settlement Execution by HKICL FPS Platform"],"testability":true,"source_type":"web"},{"page":"2","page_number":2,"requirement_type":"Functional","section":"FPS Payment Flow","title":"Settlement Result Notification to Beneficiary Bank (Step 5b)","description":"The beneficiary bank receives the settlement result from HKICL (transmission format: FIToFIPmtStsRpt (pacs.002)).","business_rules":["Transmission format must be pacs.002 (FIToFIPmtStsRpt)"],"acceptance_criteria":["Beneficiary bank receives pacs.002 message from HKICL as settlement result"],"dependencies":["Settlement Execution by HKICL FPS Platform"],"testability":true,"source_type":"web"},{"page":"2","page_number":2,"requirement_type":"Functional","section":"FPS Payment Flow","title":"Credit Notification to Payer","description":"The system informs the payer of the credit result to the beneficiary account.","business_rules":[],"acceptance_criteria":["Payer is notified of the credit result to the beneficiary account"],"dependencies":["Settlement Result Notification to Payer Bank (Step 5a)"],"testability":true,"source_type":"web"},{"page":"2","page_number":2,"requirement_type":"Functional","section":"Message Reference","title":"Message Type Reference Table","description":"A reference table listing message types, names, and layout sections for Real-time and Batch scenarios, including pacs.008 Credit Transfer, pacs.008 Account Verification, pacs.002 Account Verification Result, and pacs.002 Payment Status R