# 模块内容
{"platform":"FPS Payment System","main_module_name":"Inbound Transfer Flow","main_module_source":"Page1","submodule_name":"Transaction Transmission to HKICL - pacs.008","submodule_description":"Payer bank transmits the transaction instruction to HKICL in FIToFICustomerCreditTransfer (pacs.008) format.","submodule_source":"Page1","documentId":"273482620939927552","version":"vz30","source_type":"web","change_type":"NEW","page":"Page1"}

# 具体页面内容,存在章节内容跨页面内容.
[{"page":1,"content":"8.1.4 入賬轉賬之 successful (with account verification) 流程\n圖一\n處理流程如下：\n1. 付款戶輸入資料發動交易(經櫃檯/網上銀行/手機銀行，收款账户有FPSID、手机号码、电子邮件、账户号码)\n1.1 FPS 呼喚存款系統賬戶驗證、額度及扣賬\n1.1.1 如核對賬戶或扣賬失敗，拒納交易。如成功，繼續下列執行指示。\n2. 付款銀行傳送交易指示予 HKICL (傳送格式: FIToFICustomerCreditTransfer (pasc.008))\n3. HKICL 傳送交易予收款銀行(如收款銀行是 real-time 模式)需要有賬戶校驗，(傳送格式: FIToFICustomerCreditTransfer (pasc.008))"}]

